* Creditcard / Debitcard
* VISA / Mastercad
* Carte bancaire / Carte blue
* eMaestro / Maestro
* Neteller
* iDEAL
* Bancontact / Mister Cash
* Mybank
* Sofortbanking
* Giropay
* (online) Bank transfer
	
##Fees and rates

The website exchange rate is based on market average EUR/BTC rate +2%.<br/>
The various payment methods charge a fixed and a variable amount.<br/>

